damage to the entire pins system
malfunction or failure of GPS and Bluetooth systems.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning tailgate can cause injury to occupants or bystanders, as it may close unexpectedly, and also lead to inconvenience and difficulty in accessing the trunk.
symptoms: Tailgate does not open all the way up

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wiper arm can cause reduced visibility while driving, especially in rainy or snowy conditions, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The windshield wiper arm breaks or snaps off
the windshield wiper flies off the vehicle
the windshield wiper freezes during use
the windshield wiper hits the other wiper arm.
